title: cmd/go: TestGoGetInsecure fails
body:
At tip, run on darwin_amd64 and confirmed on a linux laptop. This test does not run in -short mode (i.e., on the builders).

```
$ go test -run GoGetInsecure
--- FAIL: TestGoGetInsecure (3.42s)
	go_test.go:244: running testgo [get -d wh3rd.net/git.git]
	go_test.go:281: testgo succeeded unexpectedly
FAIL
exit status 1
FAIL	cmd/go	9.208s
```
